text: Dino De Zordo (born 15 May 1937) is an Italian ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1960 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Italian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Italy Category:Ski jumpers at the 1960 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Veneto Category:People from the Province of Belluno
